Introduction

ANODE is a producer duo from South Korea, signed under MYSTIC Story. The pair made their debut on April 17, 2024, with the release of their digital single titled “Imagine#1 ‘Trouble’”.

The name ANODE is inspired by the physical concept of an anode, reflecting the duo’s unique dynamic where each member embodies the opposite traits of a cathode and an anode, working together to produce harmonious music.
